author: stsp
msg: Make svnrdump print progress information to stderr by default,
(svnrdump__options, main): Switch the --verbose flag to a --quiet flag.
(replay_revend): Print progress info unless we're supposed to be quiet.

author: rhuijben
msg: Simplify tempfile management in svnrdump a bit.
(window_handler): Don't close the deltafile and stream. The inner
handler closes the stream for us; and not disowning in apply_textdelta,
makes this apply to the file.
(apply_textdelta): Just open a unique stream. Don't create a disowned
